---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About VantaJax"
  description="Learn what VantaJax is, why it exists, and how it supports Black-owned businesses in Jacksonville."
>
  <section class="py-10 px-4">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl space-y-8">
      <header class="space-y-2">
        <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-purple-600">
          About
        </p>
        <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900">
          VantaJax is a radar for Black-owned businesses
        </h1>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-600">
          VantaJax is built to make it easier to find, support, and stay connected with
          Black-owned businesses, services, and professionals across Jacksonville, FL.
        </p>
      </header>

      <section class="space-y-3 text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-700">
        <h2 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-500">
          Why this exists
        </h2>
        <p>
          A lot of us want to support Black-owned spaces, but actually finding them can be
          confusing, fragmented, or based on word of mouth. VantaJax helps take out some of
          that friction by curating a focused, local-first directory that you can search and
          contribute to.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-3 text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-700">
        <h2 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-500">
          How it works
        </h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
          <li>
            <span class="font-medium">Browse:</span> search by city, ZIP, category, and
            verification status to explore the directory.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="font-medium">Suggest:</span> submit Black-owned businesses that
            should be on the radar. Submissions are reviewed before going live.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="font-medium">Verify:</span> over time, businesses can be verified
            to help build trust and confidence for the community.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-3 text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-700">
        <h2 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-500">
          Whatâ€™s next
        </h2>
        <p>
          VantaJax is starting in Jacksonville, but the long-term goal is to grow the
          platform, improve the data, and add more ways for people to discover, share, and
          support Black-owned businesses where they live.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
